    <Note Title="Topic" Type="Summary" Ordinal="1" xml:lang="en">Security update for XWayland</Note>
    <Note Title="Details" Type="General" Ordinal="2" xml:lang="en">The XWayland portion of the x.org X11 server was updated to fix one security issue.

The following vulnerability was fixed:

* CVE-2015-3164: Unauthorised local client access in XWayland (boo#934102)</Note>
